Ba jail Madhouse
===========================

Map created by Exel80 

**Games:**

- Sofa game
- Soccer
- Tetris
- Race
- Jump
- Pool
- Bhop

**Feature:**

- 2 medic
- 1 pistol + 1 flash in jail
- 1 jail secret
- Solitary confinement
- Secret buttons to open armor
- Disco (Epic music)
- Skybox
etc.
